angstd.model.workspace
Class CategoryElement

java.lang.Object
  angstd.model.workspace.WorkspaceElement
      angstd.model.workspace.CategoryElement

public class CategoryElement
extends WorkspaceElement

CategoryElement describes Workspace elements, representing categories for views respectively datasets.

In general ViewElements are assigned to those workspace elements as children and the ViewType is the backend structure to specify the view category.

Author:
Andreas Held
